how can i access the eye candy app?

Works but instructions suck, they leave out a few key elements, the main one being you have to click 'Other activation options'. Here are the revised instructions:

1. Run the installer
2. Uncheck "Register on line" click OK
3. By the first use, Eye Candy Asks for a serial,
4. Run the KeyGen, to generate a serial,
5. Copy the serial and paste in EyeCandy register box
6. Click Next
7. Click Other Activation Options
8. Copy and paste Installation ID from Eyecandy to Keygen Installation ID box
9. Click Activate (Keygen)
10. Copy and paste unlock code into Eyecandy unlock code box
11. Click Activate (Eyecandy)
12. Badabing

Works Great -- Clean with no viruses/trojans!  During installation after pasting generated serial number, and unchecking online registration, product is installed.  Open Photoshop and run an Eyecandy filter.  From there, you have the option to activate.  Copy Installation ID and Paste into Keygen.In keygen, then in the Dropdown box, select Eyecandy 6.0 which will give you the unlock code needed to complete registration process.  Woop!
